{"model": "Qwen 2.5 32B Instruct", "runtime": "llamacpp", "prompt_name": "code_fibonacci__t2_docstring", "prompt_tokens": 0, "generation_tokens": 0, "prompt_tps": 139.4, "generation_tps": 23.1, "peak_memory_gb": 0.0, "wall_time_sec": 6.2, "output": "```python\ndef fibonacci(n: int) -> int:\n    \"\"\"Return the nth Fibonacci number.\n\n    fibonacci(0) = 0\n    fibonacci(1) = 1\n    fibonacci(n) = fibonacci(n-1) + fibonacci(n-2)\n    \"\"\"\n    if n == 0:\n        return 0\n    elif n == 1:\n        return 1\n    else:\n        a, b = 0, 1\n        for _ in range(2, n + 1):\n            a, b = b, a + b\n        return b", "error": null, "prompt_hash": "529a97de5cfa"}
